56 void PioneerSIP::identify(const PioneerPacket &packet) const
57 {
58  if (packet.at(1) >= STANDARDmpac && packet.at(1) <= STANDARDMpac)
59  parseStandard(packet);
60  else {
61  switch (packet.at(1))
62  {
63  case CONFIGpac:
64  parseConfig(packet);
65  break;
66  case SERAUXpac:
67  case SERAUX2pac:
68  case SERAUX3pac:
69  parseSERAUX(packet);
70  break;
71  case ENCODERpac:
72  parseEncoder(packet);
73  break;
74  case TCM2pac:
75  parseTCM2(packet);
76  break;
77  case IOpac:
78  parseIO(packet);
79  break;
80  case IMUpac:
81  parseIMU(packet);
82  break;
83  case JOYSTICKpac:
84  parseJoystick(packet);
85  break;
86  case GRIPPERpac:
87  parseGripper(packet);
88  break;
89  case GYROpac:
90  parseGyro(packet);
91  break;
92  case ARMINFOpac:
93  parseArmInfo(packet);
94  break;
95  case ARMpac:
96  parseArm(packet);
97  break;
98  default:
99  ROS_ERROR("Could not identify packet type 0x%.2x", packet.at(1));
100  break;
101  }
102  }
103 }

105 void PioneerSIP::parseStandard(const PioneerPacket & packet) const
106 {
107  typedef std::pair<unsigned char, int> sonar_t;
108  static int total_x = 0;
109  static int total_y = 0;
110  static int total_th = 0;
111  static int prev_x = 0;
112  static int prev_y = 0;
113  static double dist_conv_factor = config_.getDouble("DistConvFactor");
114  static double angle_conv_factor = config_.getDouble("AngleConvFactor");
115  static double vel_conv_factor = config_.getDouble("VelConvFactor");
116  static double diff_conv_factor = config_.getDouble("DiffConvFactor");
117  static bool front_bumpers = config_.getBool("FrontBumpers");
118  static bool rear_bumpers = config_.getBool("RearBumpers");
119  static int num_front_bumpers = config_.getInt("NumFrontBumpers");
120  static int num_rear_bumpers = config_.getInt("NumRearBumpers");
121 
122  int index = 2;
123  int curr_x, curr_y, curr_th;
124  int vel_l, vel_r;
125  unsigned char batt;
126  std::vector<bool> l_stall_bump;
127  std::vector<bool> r_stall_bump;
128  int control;
129  std::vector<bool> flags_0_7;
130  std::vector<bool> flags_8_15;
131  unsigned char compass;
132  unsigned char sonar_count;
133  std::vector<sonar_t> sonar_readings;
134  unsigned char grip_state;
135  unsigned char analog_port;
136  unsigned char analog_reading;
137  unsigned char digital_in;
138  unsigned char digital_out;
139  int battery; // Useful when batt > 255
140  unsigned char charge_state;
141 
142  if (total_x == std::numeric_limits<int>::max())
143  total_x = 0;
144  if (total_y == std::numeric_limits<int>::max())
145  total_y = 0;
146 
147  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, curr_x);
148  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, curr_y);
149  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, curr_th);
150  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, vel_l);
151  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, vel_r);
152  batt = packet.at(index++);
153  index = packet.getBoolVectorAt(index, l_stall_bump);
154  index = packet.getBoolVectorAt(index, r_stall_bump);
155  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, control);
156  index = packet.getBoolVectorAt(index, flags_0_7);
157  index = packet.getBoolVectorAt(index, flags_8_15);
158  compass = packet.at(index++);
159  sonar_count = packet.at(index++);
160  for (int i = 0; i < sonar_count; ++i) {
161  sonar_t sonar_reading;
162  sonar_reading.first = packet.at(index++);
163  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, sonar_reading.second);
164  sonar_readings.push_back(sonar_reading);
165  }
166  grip_state = packet.at(index++);
167  analog_port = packet.at(index++);
168  analog_reading = packet.at(index++);
169  digital_in = packet.at(index++);
170  digital_out = packet.at(index++);
171  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, battery);
172  charge_state = packet.at(index);
173 
174  curr_x %= 4096;
175  curr_y %= 4096;
176 
177  int diff_x = this->encoderDifference(prev_x, curr_x);
178  int diff_y = this->encoderDifference(prev_y, curr_y);
179  prev_x = curr_x;
180  prev_y = curr_y;
181  int change_x = static_cast<int>(round(diff_x * dist_conv_factor));
182  int change_y = static_cast<int>(round(diff_y * dist_conv_factor));
183  total_x += change_x;
184  total_y += change_y;
185  total_th = static_cast<int>(round(degreesToRad(curr_th * angle_conv_factor)));
186 
187 }

231 
232  index = packet.getStringAt(index, robot_type);

234  index = packet.getStringAt(index, robot_serial_number);
235  four_motors = packet.at(index++);
236  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, top_rot_vel);

238  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, top_rot_acc);
239  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, top_trans_acc);
240  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, max_pwm);
241  index = packet.getStringAt(index, robot_name);
242  sip_cycle = packet.at(index++);
243  host_baud = packet.at(index++);
244  aux_baud = packet.at(index++);
245  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, gripper);
246  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, front_sonar);
247  rear_sonar = packet.at(index++);
248  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, low_battery);
249  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, rev_count);
250  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, watchdog);
251  p2mpacs = packet.at(index++);
252  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, stall_value);
253  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, stall_count);
254  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, joy_vel);
255  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, joy_rvel);
256  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, max_rot_vel);
257  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, max_trans_vel);
258  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, rot_accel);
259  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, rot_decel);
260  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, rot_kp);
261  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, rot_kv);
262  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, rot_ki);
263  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, trans_accel);
264  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, trans_decel);
265  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, trans_kp);
266  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, trans_kv);
267  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, trans_ki);
268  front_bumpers = packet.at(index++);
269  rear_bumpers = packet.at(index++);
270  charger = packet.at(index++);
271  sonar_cycle = packet.at(index++);
272  autobaud = packet.at(index++);
273  has_gyro = packet.at(index++);
274  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, drift_factor);
275  aux2_baud = packet.at(index++);
276  aux3_baud = packet.at(index++);
277  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, ticks_mm);
278  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, shutdown_volts);
279  // Check version
280  if (packet.at(index) != '\0') {
281  index = packet.getStringAt(index, version);
282  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, gyro_cw);
283  index = packet.getIntegerAt(index, gyro_ccw);
284  kinematics_delay = packet.at(index++);
285  }
286 }

289 {

293  int index = 2;

342 int PioneerSIP::encoderDifference(int previous, int current)
343 {
344  int diff = std::abs(current - previous);
345  int compl_diff = 4096 - diff;
346  if (current >= previous)
347  return (diff < compl_diff ? diff : compl_diff);
348  else
349  return (diff < compl_diff ? -diff : -compl_diff);
350 }

352 double PioneerSIP::radToDegrees(double radians)
353 {
354  static const double PI = boost::math::constants::pi<double>();
355  return (radians * 180.0 / PI);
